Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.00,0:01:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是赤报队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.60,0:01:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一队队长相乐对吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.13,0:01:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我乃是官军参谋进藤带刀\N前来传达总督府的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.07,0:01:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.17,0:01:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如今你们的任务已结束\N辛苦啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.28,0:01:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.46,0:02:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事过十年\N终于又是赤报队登场的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.90,0:02:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.00,0:02:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二十三话\N左之助的背叛！？命运之再会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.51,0:02:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,锦绘…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.04,0:02:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我手边的工作都放不下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.61,0:02:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，要我替你去买是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.35,0:02:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，可不可以拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.92,0:02:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂、喂，你别人不找\N想叫左之助先生打你啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.09,0:02:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，不怕死的小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.69,0:02:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.73,0:02:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊！打他的事交给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.60,0:02:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说真的啊，左之先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.93,0:02:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有关系\N老是让他请客….对吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.84,0:02:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是请\N全部都是让你欠着而已哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.37,0:02:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么不知道…\N不过我可没钱还你….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.31,0:03:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也没有期待你现在就还\N所以我有帮你算利息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.35,0:03:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备慢慢地等啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.48,0:03:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利、利息？牛肉火锅的钱\N有人算利息的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.56,0:03:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了不起！你真是商人的榜样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.76,0:03:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去….算了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.23,0:03:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那，是要买谁的，哪种画？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.20,0:03:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月冈津南画的剑客\N伊庭八郎喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.90,0:03:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幕府末期最受欢迎的剑士\N“赤靴之伊庭八”啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.77,0:03:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还看不出来\N有这种轻浮的兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.41,0:03:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么，我就去走一遭吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.78,0:03:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，对不起….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.25,0:03:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.88,0:03:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有话就说，直载了当地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.08,0:03:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雀儿….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.29,0:03:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事，真的没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.06,0:03:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此\N那么买月冈津的伊庭八二张吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.87,0:03:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是左之先生，高人一等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.67,0:04:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N如果再加上都能按照付钱给我的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.04,0:04:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然变得随和的左之先生是不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.18,0:04:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过以前的左之先生也很迷人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.35,0:04:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，打架骓“斩左”！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.02,0:04:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来，脸上带着笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.88,0:04:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心里却一点也不满足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.02,0:04:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如同将爆发的炸弹般\N总是闪闪耀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.00,0:04:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.76,0:04:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.07,0:04:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.50,0:04:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔，是两位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.04,0:04:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,买锦绘吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.87,0:04:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次听说左之助\N也有这种兴趣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.04,0:04:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是美人图吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.41,0:04:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是春画？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.65,0:04:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，不行不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.25,0:04:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌春画
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.75,0:04:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐，你在干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.85,0:04:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上信以为真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.39,0:04:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.46,0:04:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小妙红着脸拜托我的\N可不是买我自己的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.93,0:04:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老板，月冈津南的伊庭八我要两张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.70,0:05:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,津南的伊庭八是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.07,0:05:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,客人，你运气真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.40,0:05:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里，正好是最后的两张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.07,0:05:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,津南的画很受欢迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.60,0:05:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就卖光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.44,0:05:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是属于美帅型的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.81,0:05:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二张一共十钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.91,0:05:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，我没带钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.74,0:05:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐先借一点给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.68,0:05:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是，一定要还喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.02,0:05:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.38,0:05:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这东西叫作锦绘\N倒是各式各样都有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.66,0:05:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.82,0:05:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是，相乐队长….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.86,0:05:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那张啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.00,0:05:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同样是津南的画
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.13,0:05:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就只那张卖不出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.37,0:05:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而他却都一定画他\N那位冒牌官军头目的画
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.97,0:05:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月冈，住哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.57,0:05:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,津南那家伙，人在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.34,0:05:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.25,0:05:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真，真对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.28,0:05:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老先生你多说了废话….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.12,0:05:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他住隔壁村的简陋大杂房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.39,0:05:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过，那人讨厌和人来往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.49,0:05:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去了，他也不会见你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.52,0:06:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他会的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.09,0:06:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那小子不可能不见我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.79,0:06:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.60,0:06:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，好熏啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.14,0:06:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到里面去等吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.24,0:06:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿松，你回来啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.41,0:06:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小富也买了秋刀鱼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.01,0:06:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月冈先生….不在吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.78,0:06:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月冈先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.25,0:06:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月冈先生你在吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.55,0:06:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原赤报队预备队员月冈克浩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.49,0:06:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.06,0:06:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这画是你画的吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.03,0:06:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.60,0:06:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你….怎么会….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.00,0:06:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一看就知道了\N队长的身边有以前的你和我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.84,0:06:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这画，别人是画不出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.21,0:06:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此，说的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.45,0:06:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过，没想到你还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.98,0:06:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这王八蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.05,0:07:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比此比此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.92,0:07:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛…画师\N月冈津南也是赤报队残留队员啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.69,0:07:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回家吧！薰小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.16,0:07:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，剑心….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.73,0:07:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.43,0:07:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且，赤报队对左之而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.67,0:07:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有特殊的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.20,0:07:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在回忆中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.40,0:07:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,局外人是不需要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.94,0:07:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，没想到你成个画画的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.61,0:07:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过，从前你就很灵巧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.85,0:07:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使用大炮，调火药等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.72,0:07:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么难的事都能简单地做好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.86,0:07:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经十年了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.36,0:07:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,队长，相乐队长！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.07,0:07:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我准备食物来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.47,0:07:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看，大丰收！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.87,0:07:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙还不快死心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.57,0:07:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别让鱼逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.78,0:08:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,队长，这小子掉了三只鲤鱼啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.18,0:08:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说好不说的嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.45,0:08:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜，什么事都要报告队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.02,0:08:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不守信用，王八蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.16,0:08:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突击啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.37,0:08:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是幕府的兵，快起来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.24,0:08:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助，克浩！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.97,0:08:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们到安全的地方去避难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.28,0:08:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要说笑！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.84,0:08:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死也不会离开队长身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.61,0:08:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也是赤报队的一份子呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.18,0:08:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相乐队长！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.82,0:08:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们说的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.69,0:08:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.60,0:08:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿克！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.13,0:08:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没事！擦伤而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.34,0:08:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很危险的，你这王八蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.80,0:09:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么，危险的是你啊傻瓜蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.67,0:09:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了， 王八
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.91,0:09:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王八蛋和傻瓜却都还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.15,0:09:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之，你目前在作什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.76,0:09:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊，只是个流浪汉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.53,0:09:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过，顺其自然挺快乐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.96,0:09:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛，你过得挺快乐的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.40,0:09:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这十年从没快乐过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.14,0:09:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才遇到你以前从来没笑过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.34,0:09:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给相乐队长和我们赤报队\N戴上污名的那些人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.88,0:09:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我恨着他们渡过了这十年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.38,0:09:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也和你一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.75,0:09:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.35,0:09:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.55,0:09:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天，所有都准备\N万全之时能和你相会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.99,0:09:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为是队长的指引….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.79,0:09:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.10,0:09:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿克你….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.20,0:10:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助，我和你\N再次重组赤报队吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.20,0:10:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.37,0:10:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打倒陷害我们\N赤报队的维新政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.21,0:10:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实现相乐队长理想之新时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.38,0:10:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说要打倒政府….你？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.38,0:10:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的计划毫无缺点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.01,0:10:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看！我利用在赤报队学的\N检药知识所制成的炸药弹！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.85,0:10:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿克，你？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.82,0:10:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的十年！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.42,0:10:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然如此地….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.46,0:10:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用这个\N首先是内务省  然后….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.00,0:10:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来把各省厅给炸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.30,0:10:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要反政府火花在东京发动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.97,0:10:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在全国各地不平的士族和\N农民们一定会一齐响应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.54,0:10:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后，就等着看\N明治政府崩坏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.78,0:10:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有用的….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.41,0:10:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之  难道你不憎恨\N污赖我们赤报队的明治政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.42,0:10:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想把它打垮吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.39,0:10:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋东西！我当然恨明治政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.36,0:11:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，我知道\N那不是我所办得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.73,0:11:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和持续了三百年的\N德川幕府比起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.76,0:11:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明治政府也不过才十几年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.20,0:11:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凭我就能把它炸的粉碎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.94,0:11:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使你爆破成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.84,0:11:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全国也未必会一拥而起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.14,0:11:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿克，你要知道\N推翻明治政府是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.31,0:11:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之，对你而言赤报队\N似乎已是过去之事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.22,0:11:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在活得快活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.72,0:11:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也没打算再拖你下水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.45,0:11:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊克….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.76,0:11:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个王八左之已不在人世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.89,0:11:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十年来，天天想着为赤报队\N和队长洗清罪名的他而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.87,0:11:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是看不清现实的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.74,0:11:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已十年了….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.71,0:11:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他妈的，吹起冷风来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.18,0:12:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你，你们是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.59,0:12:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强，强盗啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.82,0:12:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了建设新的时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.59,0:12:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们赤报队要征收你的宝物\N作为军用资金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.09,0:12:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赤….赤报队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.21,0:12:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小雀真会拍球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.25,0:12:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也会耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.35,0:12:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这几天，已有七间被抢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.25,0:12:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使用炸裂弹，手法还真粗暴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.96,0:12:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是旧赤报队员所为吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.33,0:12:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面写着每次都有留下\N相乐队长的锦绘….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.90,0:12:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.07,0:12:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是左之助做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.63,0:12:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑，不可以乱说！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.47,0:12:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.57,0:12:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然左之助曾擅自到人家里吃饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.31,0:12:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借了钱不还
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.04,0:13:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还会白吃白喝，然后….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.78,0:13:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,岂不是没做一件好事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.18,0:13:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈！人的优点不是\N用嘴巴可以说得清的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.09,0:13:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交往过后才知道能不能信用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.12,0:13:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.56,0:13:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助即使不小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.96,0:13:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不会做那种强盗做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.76,0:13:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种事，我也知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.80,0:13:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，他一直都以\N相乐队长之事自吹自擂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.67,0:13:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是，为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.90,0:13:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相乐队长的锦绘会….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.00,0:13:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.87,0:13:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个人会不会有关连
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.61,0:13:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,画师？你是说月冈津南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.41,0:13:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望不是最好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.15,0:13:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.15,0:13:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿克！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.13,0:13:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之，能遇到你，我很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.93,0:13:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿克….不要是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.77,0:13:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.91,0:14:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿克跑到那儿去了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.28,0:14:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之先生！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.75,0:14:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银次兄怎么了，脸色都变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.05,0:14:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的，听到个奇怪传言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.89,0:14:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想应该和\N左之先生有关系….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.49,0:14:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么传言？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.82,0:14:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,据说，在西町的赌场\N有个家伙最近很阔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.46,0:14:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听那家伙说这都是\N托赤报队的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.23,0:14:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.30,0:14:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.70,0:14:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好象叫什么红鼻子的新藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.00,0:14:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,红鼻子的新藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.51,0:14:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之先生？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.77,0:14:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\N让你们为了我到处奔波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.84,0:14:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,, 下次送礼谢你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.01,0:14:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了，说什么送礼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.45,0:14:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我俩是因为迷上你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.61,0:14:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在的你和以前的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.19,0:14:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相乐队长的画？案件的事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.39,0:14:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的   不要钱都卖不出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.29,0:14:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想问什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.06,0:14:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.30,0:14:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,案件发生之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.00,0:15:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有哪家店整批地\N卖了相乐队长的画？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.67,0:15:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，最近我们同行都在说\N对面镇上画店卖了一批
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.04,0:15:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果问那店里的人就\N大概可以知道是谁买的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.57,0:15:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这么一说，倒想起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.58,0:15:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才，津南也来问同样问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.11,0:15:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月冈津南吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.99,0:15:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一点二点是丁啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.09,0:15:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又来了今天真倒霉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.37,0:15:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近新藏先生景气不错嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.37,0:15:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说你找到了摇钱树
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.30,0:15:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来是真的喽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.94,0:15:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，托赤报队财神爷的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.48,0:15:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心情不错嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.62,0:15:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,红鼻子的新藏先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.49,0:15:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁，你是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.62,0:15:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是谁，你别管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.12,0:16:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以前不是叫什么\N不知火党的强盗团的手下吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.06,0:16:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.43,0:16:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只要回答我的问题即可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.63,0:16:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁，谁要回答你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.70,0:16:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想回答，我也要你说说\N你最喜欢的赤报队的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.31,0:16:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真慢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.91,0:16:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很报歉！那小子又去\N赌场了吧.去叫来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.72,0:16:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.78,0:16:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.12,0:16:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天要抢的对象是….！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.69,0:16:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.65,0:16:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,油类的大盘，清水屋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.99,0:16:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是清水屋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.09,0:16:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以收集美术品出名的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.53,0:16:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们拿得到的份\N这次似乎会很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.20,0:16:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩，日本的美术品\N很受横滨外国人贸易商喜爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.34,0:16:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以卖很多钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.27,0:16:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么….警察方面呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.14,0:16:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们以为是旧赤报队干的\N正拼命地在找寻残党呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.65,0:17:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越想越觉得赤报队的人\N真是可悲啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.22,0:17:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是维新志士，又是警察干部\N进藤先生，我们也能够安泰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.92,0:17:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起来进藤先生\N才算是真正的坏人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.86,0:17:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想一生\N在警察局当公务员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.63,0:17:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个时代钱最好用\N我还需要更多的钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.57,0:17:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以只好让赤报队\N继续当坏人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.47,0:17:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新藏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.51,0:17:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老大….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.94,0:17:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.24,0:17:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到，你竟成了\N不知火党的头目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.15,0:17:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用赤报队的名义抢钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.85,0:17:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原官军参谋，进藤带刀先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.45,0:17:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这位陷害相乐队长\N和我们赤报队的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.76,0:17:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小子，你到底是….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.26,0:17:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原赤报队予备队员\N相乐左之助！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.36,0:17:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么！相乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.13,0:17:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原赤报队！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.13,0:17:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你靠捉到相乐队长的功劳\N升为警察干部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.24,0:17:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却利用赤报队….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.04,0:17:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底作弄我们赤报队几次\N你才甘心，绝对不饶你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.94,0:18:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气，把他给我杀了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.69,0:18:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就你这二招还想….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.45,0:18:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！到外面去好好跟你们玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.10,0:18:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动作还真快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.88,0:18:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畜生，眼睛闭起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.32,0:18:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畜生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.85,0:18:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在，杀了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.36,0:18:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.46,0:18:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追查收购相乐队长画的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.26,0:18:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于被我找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.13,0:18:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些冒牌的赤报队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.80,0:18:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.40,0:19:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿克，让他们好好的看看\N真正的赤报队打架的样子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.38,0:19:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.08,0:19:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.32,0:19:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畜生！你根本不是对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.49,0:19:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,料理好了，左之….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.30,0:19:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些杂鱼都料理好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.77,0:19:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就是你了进藤带刀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.78,0:19:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你们原赤报队员的尸体\N放在犯罪现场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.98,0:19:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚好作为是原赤报队\N做的最佳证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.38,0:19:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你们特地前来，谢啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.76,0:19:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.46,0:19:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.99,0:19:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿克！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.40,0:20:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混帐家伙….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.27,0:20:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧！啊克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.91,0:20:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心，擦伤而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.18,0:20:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过了十年，你还是个傻瓜蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.21,0:20:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错，而你也还是个王八蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.05,0:20:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这里，这间房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.56,0:20:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绕到后院去，快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.09,0:20:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.09,0:20:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.00,0:20:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为听说抢仓库\N是使用炸裂弹…..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.27,0:20:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，以为是我干的，是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.47,0:20:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.54,0:20:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认为我会生气吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.10,0:20:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.44,0:20:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么，干嘛道歉呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.84,0:20:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之，记住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.28,0:20:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要打倒的是明治政府\N象进藤那种利用我们赤报队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.42,0:20:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用相乐队长横行霸道的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.99,0:21:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后，建立真正\N四民平等的时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.83,0:21:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如此而已，再见了，傻瓜蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.57,0:21:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！王八蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.10,0:21:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,象你这种王八蛋\N我可不会让你一个人去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.87,0:21:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.11,0:21:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行动之日决定了，通知我吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.08,0:21:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之你这嚣张的傻瓜蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.25,0:21:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在的朋友虽然重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.88,0:21:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是和以前的朋友比起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.72,0:21:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不得不舍弃现在的所有……
